After a very long time...a show like "Arrow" have been telecast-ed...this show has everything for one who is fond of viewing Batman like superhero series.Very good acting,direction is excellent,cinematography is too good.It's a complete package TV show.Plot of this show is so refreshing,excellent that you will get addict to this show.This show is for the one's who are tired of watching shows who have slow plots,supernatural activities,extreme comedy etc.Once you have watched "pilot"..your excitement will grow even more and one would want to see all the episodes one after another.1st season has been up to the mark.Hope to have a glance of 2nd season soon.